# Implementation Plan - Enrich AulaPlanejamentoEstrategico.tsx

The goal is to expand the content of the strategic planning class to provide a premium experience while meeting the requirement of exceeding 2500 lines. This will be achieved by adding technical depth, more practice questions, and fixing identified gaps.

## Proposed Changes

### [Component] AulaPlanejamentoEstrategico.tsx

#### [MODIFY] [AulaPlanejamentoEstrategico.tsx](file:///c:/Workspace/petrobras-quest/src/components/aulas/administracao/AulaPlanejamentoEstrategico.tsx)

- **Enrich "Nota Técnica: A Governança Blindada"**: Fill the empty grid at line 2296 with 4 detailed cards about:
  1. Segregação de Funções.
  2. Comitês de Assessoramento.
  3. Divulgação de Informações (CVM).
  4. Auditoria e Controle Interno.
- **Expand "Banco de Questões"**: Add 20 new high-level questions (41-60) focusing on:
  1. BSC in the public sector.
  2. BANI/VUCA scenarios.
  3. 13.303/16 legal nuances.
  4. Petrobras PE 2024-2028 specifics (CAPEX/Decarbonization).
- **Add "Dicas de Estudo Expresso"**: Insert small aesthetic banners between major sections to provide extra tips and increase line count.
- **Deepen "Estudo de Caso Master"**: Add a "Resolução Sugerida" sub-section to the case study to provide pedagogical value.

